OL,3,CPolls open in Makerfield by-election
OL,5,FPolling stations have opened in a by-
OL,6,Felection that will see Makerfield's
OL,7,Fnext MP elected.
OL,9,FFourteen candidates are standing for
OL,10,Fthe seat which became vacant after the
OL,11,Fresignation of Labour's Josh Simons.
OL,13,FPeople are reminded to take a valid
OL,14,Fphoto ID with them, and have until
OL,15,F10pm to cast their vote.
